      <title>谈判仍在继续，大众汽车罢工将于 12 月开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vw-warning-strikes-to-start-in-december-as-talks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于工会领袖和管理层未能就如何削减该汽车制造商同名品牌的成本达成协议，德国各地大众汽车工人计划从下月初开始举行大规模罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vw-warning-strikes-to-start-in-december-as-talks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
