    <item>
      <title>埃尔德森称欧洲央行不能简单地“忽视”供应冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/ecb-cannot-simply-look-through-supply-shocks-elderson-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执行委员会成员弗兰克·埃尔德森表示，欧洲央行再也不能忽视供给冲击对经济的影响，因为它们可能对通胀产生持久影响，并补充说，未来这种冲击可能会更频繁地出现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/ecb-cannot-simply-look-through-supply-shocks-elderson-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 15:34:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Two Sigma 新任联席首席执行官裁员 10% 引起轰动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-21/two-sigma-s-new-co-ceos-make-a-splash-with-10-staff-cut-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Hema Parmar 表示，Two Sigma 裁员 10% 标志着这家对冲基金的联席首席执行官自 9 月成立以来首次发生重大转变，此前两位创始人之间发生了激烈的争执。她在“彭博未平仓头寸”节目中发表了讲话。Sonali Basak 的“华尔街快讯”通讯于周五发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-21/two-sigma-s-new-co-ceos-make-a-splash-with-10-staff-cut-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 15:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
